en_6020088_0	Colombo (News 1st) – Three-wheel prices will be reduced by Rs.
en_6020088_1	10 with effect from Midnight tomorrow (December 02).
en_6020088_2	Sunil Jayawardena, Chairman of the National Association of Self-employed Professionals said that the charge for the first Kilometre was reduced from Rs.
en_6020088_3	60 to Rs.
en_6020088_4	50.
en_6020088_5	He noted that this change came about due to the reduction of fuel prices.
en_6020088_6	He further said that the Consumer Affairs Authority will take legal action against drivers who do not reduce the three wheel prices by midnight tomorrow.
